@Lee No, we haven’t fine tuned wither of the models. The quality of the answer is a function of three factors:
1. quality of input prompt 
2. selection of right chunks to pass as context 
3. output generated by the model 
The difference between performance of GPT 3.5 and GPT 4 comes mainly from step 3. Our strategy, especially for long docs in Converse app, is the same otherwise. e.g. we haven’t been using longer context window while using GPT-4.

@Hari @Rafal @vineeth to confirm.
